  <description><![CDATA[<p><strong>New</strong> for winter <strong>2012/13</strong> the Art Hotel Anterleghes in under new management and has been completely refurbished using a traditional mix of mountain woods and natural materials in a modern design. The newly designed furnishings in the public rooms and bedrooms give the hotel a contemporary edge in keeping with the new art hotel theme. Offering gourmet cuisine and an extensive wine list the Art Hotel is committed to deliver excellent services in a relaxed and informal atmosphere. Located 1 km from Selva resort centre guests are able to use the public ski bus to reach the main lifts.</p>]]></description>
